texts.text: Sacha is a character in the Minecraft Mini-Series and part of Team Tundra with Rudi.

Sacha has short black hair tied up, blue eyes with a scar across one, and copper colored skin. She wears a blue jumper, a green coat or jerkin laced up or fastened the middle, a white shawl, and brown gloves, boots, and belt.
Sacha is serious, ambitious, and likes to do things effectively. She likes the snow and tundra; and doesn't like creepers, distractions, or danger.
Sacha is based on the "Tundra Hunter" from Matel which in turn was based on a skin by the same name in the Biome Settlers Skin Pack 1.

The "Tundra Hunter" is what Sacha was based on.
